snippet.textDisplay: This is by far one of the most inspiring video on YouTube. For one, I wasn't allowed to even stray on the thought that hearing is a disability. Its a remarkable achievement that they successfully enhanced the way one should look at things. Second, Amusingly I wanted to sit on that chair and feel the sound. Honestly, the look in their eyes was enchanting enough to tell me that I would never feel the music the way they did. Their eyes talk, I have never seen so much happiness oozing except from this 4 minutes and 12 seconds of pure magic. Kudos.
